      "description": "Presenting a breathtaking, showroom-standard vehicle that serves as a benchmark for automotive preservation. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or parking lot blemish. All factory trim remains supple and dark, and the alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-total tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather seats show no signs of compression or wear, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature, from the infotainment interface to the ambient lighting, operates with the precision of a new vehicle. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified specialists. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the moment it rolled off the assembly line. Complete service records and both original keys are included.",
